{"tid":131184,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"精液當藥引！人妻傻當「榨汁機」救母病：他認識大仙","createTime":"2017-02-23T01:46:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-23T02:16:22.000Z","uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e9fbe85864a452e1e9691ef735feb659e2a29735","tid":131184,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T01:46:51.000Z","msg":"大陸北京出現一名自稱「大仙朋友」的鄧姓男子，說中張姓人妻的婚姻狀況，取信後再謊稱要拿精液當藥引，騙財騙色。張女後來警醒，報警抓人。<br />\n<br />\n鄧男宣稱是「大仙」的朋友，透過神力可以改善張女的婚姻，不過需要一些「處理費」；他事後也說中張女會離婚。這些「準確預言」讓女方對他深信不疑，予取予求。騙完了財接著是身體；他先以張女母親的病情當藉口，只要做愛拿取精液，就可以當作藥引。<br />\n<br />\n鄧男事後仍不滿足，聲稱已經離婚並與張女共度下半輩子。不過，他仍然與妻子一同生活、居住。張女這時才驚覺受騙，憤而報警。法官判決，鄧男騙取6萬多人民幣（約台幣30萬），最後以詐騙罪判2年刑期、罰金2千人民幣（約台幣1萬元）。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/jgh93IM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fjgh93IM.gif&h=e9887ce2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"770de8cc8c267616ff3f1e9ae118d3be3862d271","tid":131184,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T01:53:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"955f1539953bb3bd7f7a2a362126d335ba95ebec","tid":131184,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T01:56:33.000Z","msg":"好掛住樓主"},{"pid":"1940ced7d7e23f172faca0fbd6f266ddaaeb7ee5","tid":131184,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T02:01:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好掛住樓主</blockquote><br />\nN賓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1452956e0be45a20b3aff2bb03bde113ae74c8fd","tid":131184,"uid":75441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T02:02:28.000Z","msg":"艾巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e301a458f8c0b15ad707da6903fc6ed6526ed9d","tid":131184,"uid":4706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T02:16:22.000Z","msg":"呃6萬罰2千<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}